race.description: H&M Refridgeration Country Boosted Maiden Handicap
race.comment: CHASING QUIVERS (9) ran a couple of decent races over today's trip, including a game third here after leading three back, but failed at 1100m last time. Worth another chance back in this more suitable assignment. Some unraced runners will attract interest, headed by EEZITOSORT (6), a Tassort filly who won her latest trial at Tamworth. Looks above average. HIGHLAND DANCER (7) appears for the first time and hails from the Stirling Osland yard. Won at Armidale at her only trial appearance. Must be respected. DEEP PURPLE REIGN (5) looks ready for her first race start after a narrow defeat at Tamworth recently at her only public appearance. SPELLECAST (2) placed in a trial at Tamworth and is another facing the starter for the first time who is worth keeping tabs on.
